values: so guess what   life is quite intersting right now   my comp has finally stopped bein fucked up  ive also been dealin with a whole lot of stuff with women lately   so its been ok  ive also been talkin to someone who i have never been expectin to talk to  and i will tell u it is an amazing experience  theyre awesome  and i cant wait til next school year   thank you to everyone who has helped me though my hard times

SCHOOL IS OUT!  WOOOOOOO HOOOOOOO   Im so happy that there is no school for three months.  Its pretty cool, but i need a break.  I have met so many new people there.  Nobody really understands all the changes that i went through this year because of WHS nor do they understand how meaningful some of the experiences i have had are to me.  I am so glad to have all of you with me.  Idk what i would do without all of my friends to back me up when i was down and what i would do without people in general to make life interesting.  I'm gonna be pretty busy this summer, so let me know whats goin on whenever you can so we can hang out.  Hope everyone has a great summer.  Quote: Claire- You know what I just realized?  We have no homework tonight!!........wow.............GREAT OBSERVATION

Hey people.  Guess what?  I HAVE A LIVE JOURNAL NOW!!!  Isnt that awesome??  I know it is.  I'm happy as hell  lol  well  i hope to be able to write in this a lot.  It will be very useful.  Right now  I would like to thank a few people for what they've done for me recently.  Matt, Brandon, Jess, Billie- all the power to ya.  Keep it up!
